Genetic architecture underlying IgG-RF production is distinct from that of IgM-RF.
 We found a unique genetic architecture of IgG-RF(-) RA, which showed a strong association with the SE allele less frequent among Japanese but the most frequent in Europeans. The findings could shed light on uncovered RA pathology.
